<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2305:2328'>周禮夏官司弓矢大䘮共明弓矢<span class='krp-note'>注明噐/之用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2328:2335'>　　　頌琴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2335:2358'>春秋左傳襄公二年夏齊姜薨初穆姜使擇美檟以自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2358:2381'>為櫬與頌琴季文子取以葬君子曰非禮也禮無所逆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2381:2414'>婦養姑者也虧姑以成婦逆莫大焉<span class='krp-note'>注穆姜成公母齊/姜成公婦櫬棺也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2414:2462'><span class='krp-note'>頌琴琴名猶言雅琴皆欲以送終文疏琴瑟必以歌詩/詩有雅頌故以頌為琴名櫬琴同  知皆欲以送終也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2462:2488'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0051', 'WYG', '097-5a' );" name="097-5a" class="pb">[097-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2488:2525'>　<span class='krp-note'>顧湄曰頌琴明噐之屬即既夕有燕樂噐/周官廞樂噐檀弓琴瑟張而不平是也</span></span><br/>
